        "$$\n",
        "[S(0)-\\mathrm{e}^{-rT}D]\\mathrm{N}(d_1')-\\mathrm{e}^{-rT}K\\mathrm{N}(d_2')\\; ,\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\n",
        "where $d_1'$ and $d_2'$ are defined in @eq-americancalld1 - @eq-americancalld2.\n",
        "On the other hand, if \n",
        "$$\n",
        "D-K > -\\mathrm{e}^{-r(T'-T)}K\\;,\n",
        "$$\n",
