        "\\end{multline} \n",
        "$$ {#eq-americancall}\n",
        "\n",
        "where $d_1$ and $d_2$ are defined in @eq-americancalld1star - @eq-americancalld2star and $d_1'$ and $d_2'$ are defined in @eq-americancalld1 - @eq-americancalld2.\n",
